OL,5, Plans to move away from using hotels to
OL,6, house asylum seekers and instead place 
OL,7, them on ferries, barges and ex-military
OL,8, bases are set to be unveiled by the    
OL,9, government on Wednesday.               
OL,11,FImmigration minister Robert Jenrick is 
OL,12,Fto make the announcement, billed as a  
OL,13,F"move to rudimentary accommodation".   
OL,15,FThe UK says it is spending #6.2m a day 
OL,16,Fon hotels for asylum seekers.          
OL,18,FHowever the plans, and the new         
OL,19,Flocations themselves are likely to     
OL,20,Fprove controversial.                   
